{"tid":1258274,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"分享Win T9筆劃輸入法(免安裝)","createTime":"2019-06-26T04:36:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-08T13:52:09.000Z","uid":206090,"like":52,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":42,"replies":[{"pid":"72fea480ce4b5fff02c5405096521592ac73e46a","tid":1258274,"uid":206090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T04:36:46.000Z","msg":"v1 版本 下載：<br />\n<a href=\"https://mega.nz/#!6ToASAxD!nxGYNNVCYnU8q8FuPTnSnnLXUK0bvtP9AoF7svc3Woo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmega.nz%2F%23%216ToASAxD%21nxGYNNVCYnU8q8FuPTnSnnLXUK0bvtP9AoF7svc3Woo&d=BBPgAQHQe62%2Fb%2Fw120tVmWipy2YcCk4ac690EPkq9Sw%3D&h=3d7251a6\" target=\"_blank\">https://mega.nz/#!6ToASAxD!nxGYNNVCYnU8q8FuPTnSnnLXUK0bvtP9AoF7svc3Woo</a><br />\n自己整既，我自己己經用左三年以上，一路用一路改一路完善。<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">自此無用過九方速成。</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依家分享比大家用。唔會太專業，但應該夠日常使用。<br />\n有使用上的問題可以留言同我講。<br />\n用過既幫手share同推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n===========================<br />\n<strong>重要功能介紹：</strong><br />\n- 免安裝版，即開即用，公司機都用到<br />\n- 輸入方法與手機T9相同，只要懂得漢字筆順就打到<br />\n- 有通配符（萬能key）：L (小寫)<br />\n- 會按打字次數調整出字排序<br />\n- 打完一個字會有後續字選擇<br />\n- 有打繁出簡功能<br />\n- 有反查筆劃功能<br />\n- Windows XP、7、10都無問題<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins><span style=\"color: red;\">使用說明：</span></ins></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://1.bp.blogspot.com/-8jIxA4Jqimg/XRLkMP2O50I/AAAAAAABbyU/ptCaK5HSfW8IH90s2UwLrGxD2ld5aLXswCLcBGAs/s1600/G6Mac_keyboard_UIOJKL%2B%25281%2529.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F1.bp.blogspot.com%2F-8jIxA4Jqimg%2FXRLkMP2O50I%2FAAAAAAABbyU%2FptCaK5HSfW8IH90s2UwLrGxD2ld5aLXswCLcBGAs%2Fs1600%2FG6Mac_keyboard_UIOJKL%252B%2525281%252529.png&h=71245c95&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n* uiojklp 皆使用英文小標<br />\n- 打碼後用數字鍵(英文鍵對上一排)選字。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>快捷鍵：</strong><br />\n輸入法啟用/關閉： Ctrl + 空白鍵 <br />\n中/英模式切換： 左Shift鍵<br />\n輸入法切換： Ctrl + Down <br />\n半/全型切換 ： Shift + 空白鍵<br />\n取消已輸入的碼： ESC<br />\n<br />\n<strong>Bug:</strong><br />\n- 有時會無端端打唔到字，重開就得。<br />\n- 如果Chrome開太多視窗(不是分頁)，有時可能打唔到字，不常見，未知點解。<br />\n- 有咩問題：先重開，都唔得就留言。<br />\n<br />\n更多資料或留意日後更新，請留意：<br />\n<a href=\"https://t9input.blogspot.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft9input.blogspot.com%2F&d=BBPgAQHQe62%2Fb%2Fw120tVmWipy2YcCk4ac690EPkq9Sw%3D&h=33670d24\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t9input.blogspot.com/</a><br />\n==============================<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">Rmk. 輸入法引擎(軟件)唔係我整，我所做既係整左個T9筆劃既碼表(用Python，有人問先再講下)，整合入去個軟件(yong輸入法)再搞設定同微調。</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">唔洗多謝 但幫手推同比個like 話曬都用左我唔小時間</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"891bb38aef88b72be82d4c952e5ac297fb4ee39b","tid":1258274,"uid":55597,"like":0,"dislike":10,"score":-10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T05:39:49.000Z","msg":"linux 版？"},{"pid":"47df8e248b74ac791c04c6cc1db2ebf63cd61ec5","tid":1258274,"uid":206090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T08:24:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>linux 版？</blockquote><br />\n有諗過 亦移植到 但無時間做。"},{"pid":"8c56332c1d7665c5f331b4aa6de691d5a86249ef","tid":1258274,"uid":123497,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T09:29:22.000Z","msg":"source?"},{"pid":"372781b4666c76d473ba4470ca0535dcc4795111","tid":1258274,"uid":206090,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T09:33:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>source?</blockquote><br />\n字碼表係/mb/T9.txt。<br />\n而輸入法引擎可search 小小輸入法搵source code。"},{"pid":"aecf03dea7c57920feccad4777e78c5f91eda05c","tid":1258274,"uid":206090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedB